data.description: Need room to entertain? Love country living? With this home, you can have the best of both worlds! This 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home on 13.15 acres. Want to go fishing? Just walk to your pond in the backyard. If you're looking to hunt your own land you can in the wooded acreage in the back! When looking to entertain outside you can enjoy your company while serving everything at your outdoor kitchen and then store all of your inground pool supplies in the pool house with a 1/2 bath. Also, outside you will find a basketball court, carport, metal cover, and storage shed. Inside you will find 4 bedrooms, one being the master bedroom including a master bath en-suite with a double sink, shower, tub, and large closet with built-in storage shelves. OWNER FINANCING AVAILABLE!!! Also seller willing to sell/owner finance home and 3.159 by itself!
